[[File:Peds Lod Distance = 100.png|200px|thumb|right|100 units]]
[[File:Peds Lod Distance = 500.png|200px|thumb|right|500 units]]

==Syntax== 
<syntaxhighlight lang="lua">bool setPedsLODDistance ( float distance )</syntaxhighlight> 

===Required arguments=== 
*'''distance:''' the new peds LOD distance. This value is clamped to '''0''' â€“ '''500'''. (Default for ''high_detail_peds'' on is '''500''', when off, it is '''60''').

===Returns===
This function returns ''true'' if the argument is valid. Returns ''false'' otherwise.

==Example==
This example sets the peds LOD distance to 120.
<syntaxhighlight lang="lua">setPedsLODDistance( 120 )</syntaxhighlight>

